layoutDesc.layout: Columns: 1; ruled lines: 32; written lines: 32; Uniform layout. Catchwords from folio to folio. Large square initial words and titles. Additions and comments in the margin. Running titles.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Oriental semi-cursive and square script of the 16th century.
